          "correct": true
        },
        {
          "text": "$23$",
          "why": "Swapped the values, substituting $a=5$ and $b=4$ to get $15+8$."
        },
        {
          "text": "$17$",
          "why": "Treated $2b$ as just $b$, adding 5 instead of $2\\times 5$."
        },
        {
          "text": "$14$",
          "why": "Dropped the pronumeral $b$, evaluating $2b$ as $2$ to get $12+2$."
